Program: Outlook
Title: Bernard Baran's Conviction Appeal
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbry1
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The case of Bernard Baran, and his appeal against a conviction for child sex abuse at a daycare centre. Also on the programme chef Robert Wood who cooks in his sleep; people forced to move home, including evacuees from Chernobyl and married life in the armed forces. Presenter: Fredrick Dove. Note: in 2009 the charges against Bernard Baran were set aside. Show less